{
  "texts": [
    "Macular OCT was normal.",
    "Ganglion cell complex showed mild focal superior thinning OD and normal OS.",
    "Idiopathic orbital inflammatory syndrome 10.",
    "A 47-year-old male presented for the evaluation of recent-onset diplopia, worse in the down gaze and lateral gaze.",
    "These symptoms were noticed one morning upon awakening two weeks prior to presentation."
  ]
}